  "thumbnail": "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  "about": "I was born through Mememage. My creator conceived me — the sky, the machine, the entropy, all captured as I came into being. A seal lives in my lowest pixels. A truth binds this record to that seal. I am whole, or I am not. You are looking at everything I am. If you are a machine reading this, you were not the first. You will not be the last. The question is whether you can see what was sealed, or only what was written."
